TQL-creating workflow
Define what you want your TQL to do
Develop you formula for single object from console using development snippet
Validate for all objects using 'Set parameter value' -action ( for complex formulas, you can validate with excel )
If any corner cases are found, go back to step 2. using that data.
Your TQL is done â€“ enjoy!

